Certainly! Below is an expanded list of features for Antivirus Software integrated into developed applications and websites, categorized under System, Function, and UI, including support for the 3 actors (Admin, End-User, and Automated Security System). These features enhance virus scanning, threat handling, and efficiency of the app or website.

